Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  藤花  到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,2 点都没睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,紧张得 4 点才睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就只睡了 3 小时出头吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可能要不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,和子肯定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是我这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,预估分数才到 C 档
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,12 月的模拟考试难过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,再说你在那之后不是特别发奋学习了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,自从扭曲的彩虹消失  已经过去了一年多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们升上了高三
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,全身心投入备考一整年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就是总决战了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,vacant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,空的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,sceptical
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怀疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,reluctant
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  不情愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,intensive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两人为了接受考试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从考试前一天起住进了东京的商务旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,先在新御茶水站下车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,换乘丸之内线... 换乘不了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是要徒步走到御茶水啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那要重新买票吗...
